[Student "S"]
{WEST has a poor 9 points, but does have two 4-card Majors. So he uses Stayman.

When EAST bids \Ss, WEST isn't strong enough to bid game herself, so she temporizes 
with a 3\S invitation.

EAST has a full 17 points so he accepts the invitation.}

