{WEST, with a 5-card AND a 4-card Major first uses Stayman.

EAST denies a 4-card Major, so WEST realizes that \Ss are out. 
He then bids \Hs, promising five of them.

EAST not only has three \Hs, she also has 17 points so 
she bids 4\H.}

